<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Interview Invitation</title>
</head>
<body>
    <p>Dear <%= first_name %> <%= last_name %>,</p>
    <p>You have been invited for an interview for the <strong><%= job_title %></strong> position at <strong><%= job_company %></strong>.</p>

    <h2>Interview Details:</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Date and Time:</strong> <%= formatDate(proposed_time) %></li>
      <li><strong>Format:</strong> <%= is_online ? 'Online' : 'On-site' %></li>
      <% if (!is_online) { %>
        <li><strong>City:</strong> <%= city %></li>
        <li><strong>Street Address:</strong> <%= street_address %></li>
      <% } %>
    </ul>

    <p>Please confirm your attendance by clicking one of the links below:</p>
    <p>
      <a href="<%= confirm_link %>">Confirm Attendance</a>
      <br>
      <a href="<%= reject_link %>" class="reject">Reject Invitation</a>
    </p>

    <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out. We look forward to meeting you!</p>
</body>
</html>
